{"tid":938484,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 有囡囡約我禮拜五去睇流星雨","createTime":"2018-12-12T10:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T15:56:08.000Z","uid":199590,"like":15,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5d76e9a25a0ecd1991507b86fe9f92dcf8f76420","tid":938484,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"佢無啦啦問我禮拜五同唔同佢去西貢睇流星雨<br />\n<br />\n佢=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢 : 禮拜五得唔得閒? 可唔可以陪我去睇流星雨?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我 : 癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  噉撚凍 喺屋企瞓陣好過啦 夜啲仲要睇阿記歐霸<br />\n佢 : 吓 哦 噉好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人答到我到底流星雨有咩噉好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過係一堆星飛過之麻 點解啲女會覺得好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果嗰日多雲 仲要分分鐘無得睇 喺度食西北風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb1b41563471f25c313d9c5feb4bcc690354258","tid":938484,"uid":25568,"like":20,"dislike":106,"score":-86,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"好撚on9, 每篇文都標佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但內文又佢又我<br />\n 啲legend標黎都廢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6cbc086837d7456af7265ae37350ec7a74fdd1","tid":938484,"uid":203183,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T10:55:24.000Z","msg":"唔怪得你仲係青頭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584b867c7b7e815d9bf94a3e25c54e27fe090e1a","tid":938484,"uid":199590,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"edb1b41563471f25c313d9c5feb4bcc690354258","tid":93848